    <p>“The chem­istry and com­fort level were just right. Mark is a can-do guy. Some of his ideas are rad­i­cal, but he man­aged to con­vince us that they’d work.</p>
    <p>And they did,” says   ran­cis.</p>
    <p>The most rad­i­cal was the com­plete al­ter­ation o   the   oor plan to stream­line zoning and shape a com­pelling spa­tial jour­ney that would re  ect the home­own­ers  per­son­al­i­ties. “Fran­cis and  ichele  s pre  ious home had a   ery   ali­nese   i  e.  hile they didn  t set out to repli­cate the style, they did want a proper place for key fur­ni­ture pieces they had   rought o  er,   shares</p>
