    <p>Glass slid­ing doors with a ri    ed tex­ture sim­i­lar to the li  ing area  s stor­age walls sep­a­rate the kitchen from the rest of the home. When closed o  , it is a pri  ate working space. When opened, it is an ex­ten­sion of the li  ing room. “We cook, so the kitchen needs to   e a  le to con­tain the fumes,  ex­plains  Fran­cis.</p>
